WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: ZoXIQNIL1FA

NOTE Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.800
I welcome many people here who have not attended a program of Sri Mataji Nirmala Devi.

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:14.800
By good fortune, we are holding a seminar here this weekend

00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:20.480
and we had the idea to open it out to a wider public

00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:29.280
to share with you the remarkable discovery which is Sahaja Yoga.

00:00:40.080 --> 00:00:49.120
Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi is an absolutely unique figure in this world

00:00:49.120 --> 00:00:59.920
and people have come from many European countries to join us this weekend.

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:09.920
I'm going to ask Gregoire de Kalbermatten,

00:01:13.600 --> 00:01:16.597
who is a Swiss national,

00:01:19.377 --> 00:01:26.030
who has written a book on the subject of Sri Mataji's advent,

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:37.680
to make a presentation before Shri Mataji arrives to give you some orientation about

00:01:40.350 --> 00:01:52.030
and why it is that this is such a unique opportunity for all of us

00:01:49.360 --> 00:01:59.200
at this juncture in our history, in the national history,

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:05.200
in the international history, in the very evolution of our species.

00:02:06.724 --> 00:02:14.240
You may hear some big words this evening,

00:02:14.860 --> 00:02:28.303
but I hope that you are people of a calibre to seek the reality, the truth, in big words

00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:36.160
and not to be satisfied with superficial answers to sublime questions.

00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:47.391
We have been having an intensely joyful seminar.

00:02:50.080 --> 00:02:51.545
We want to share that joy with you.

00:02:53.975 --> 00:03:00.160
There is a very specific way by which that joy can be shared by everyone.

00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:09.920
It's the birthright of everyone. It's nothing especially abnormal.

00:03:10.500 --> 00:03:16.660
Everyone has the potential within them to achieve what has been promised.

00:03:24.440 --> 00:03:36.435
And we hope very much that later on you will make a point of finding out for yourself,

00:03:36.605 --> 00:03:48.160
individually, how much potential you have to transform into the promised state,

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:55.360
which is very blissful, very peaceful and very nourishing,

00:03:58.340 --> 00:04:01.798
which we call Self-realisation.

00:04:04.038 --> 00:04:07.980
After the programme, those who are interested to do so

00:04:08.010 --> 00:04:14.728
may like to leave their name and address with us in the foyer

00:04:14.898 --> 00:04:19.184
so that we can be in touch with you about other programmes.

00:04:19.444 --> 00:04:25.324
Programmes are held regularly in London and in many other cities in this country.

00:04:25.664 --> 00:04:29.324
And we look forward to meeting you and getting to know you.

00:04:29.864 --> 00:04:37.206
So without further ado, I'll ask Gregoire to speak to you

00:04:37.390 --> 00:04:42.486
and to introduce Shri Mataji who will be here in a few minutes. Thank you.

00:05:06.320 --> 00:05:08.320
All right, it's working.

00:05:09.280 --> 00:05:15.280
Again, good evening to everybody and most welcome.

00:05:15.280 --> 00:05:21.280
It's a very nice surroundings, we had a very jolly weekend here.

00:05:21.280 --> 00:05:25.280
And we thank you for coming this evening.

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:35.280
Now, introducing Sahaja Yoga or Shri Mataji is always a privilege,

00:05:35.440 --> 00:05:40.240
although it's not a very easy topic.

00:05:40.240 --> 00:05:45.840
The reason it is not an easy topic is that the subject matter

00:05:45.840 --> 00:05:53.600
is slightly beyond the borders of our wildest dreams.

00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:58.080
And while presenting it, we have to be very careful not to look

00:05:58.080 --> 00:06:03.200
like somebody who would be naive to the point of idiocity.

00:06:03.280 --> 00:06:05.280
Is it an English word, idiocity?

00:06:05.280 --> 00:06:07.280
Okay.

00:06:07.280 --> 00:06:10.800
Because what we are talking about is self-realisation.

00:06:10.800 --> 00:06:14.080
If any of us know what self-realisation is about,

00:06:14.080 --> 00:06:16.080
then we know it's a very big thing.

00:06:18.080 --> 00:06:24.080
It is something that very few saints and sages of the olden days

00:06:24.080 --> 00:06:28.880
used to achieve after lives of tremendous labours and penances

00:06:28.880 --> 00:06:30.880
dedicated to that very purpose,

00:06:30.880 --> 00:06:35.760
which obviously is not the situation in which I am finding myself.

00:06:35.760 --> 00:06:39.920
I am an international civil servant, I have a wife, three children and so on.

00:06:39.920 --> 00:06:41.760
So that keeps me pretty busy.

00:06:44.560 --> 00:06:51.520
So, self-realisation while living in the world, this sounds like utopia.

00:06:52.720 --> 00:06:55.520
I have met Shri Mataji about 10 years ago,

00:06:56.960 --> 00:06:59.920
slightly more I suppose now,

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:05.042
and that is enough for me to know it's not utopia, it's reality.

00:07:05.200 --> 00:07:09.932
Now, I have no pretension to communicate this very truth to you,

00:07:11.120 --> 00:07:15.040
because if I have accepted it, it is on the basis of my own experience

00:07:15.040 --> 00:07:17.360
and not because anybody would tell me so.

00:07:17.360 --> 00:07:19.200
Actually the people who told me so,

00:07:19.200 --> 00:07:24.140
I told them that they were, you know, kidding themselves.

00:07:24.320 --> 00:07:29.100
And I would expect from you the same kind of healthy scepticism.

00:07:29.920 --> 00:07:32.000
I.e. you shouldn't believe me of course.

00:07:34.320 --> 00:07:38.960
Somebody who believes people in this world today is somebody who is in for troubles,

00:07:38.960 --> 00:07:42.240
because especially in the field of spirituality,

00:07:42.960 --> 00:07:45.920
you have all kinds of crazy shows going on in town.

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:49.600
Unfortunately these shows are sometimes very successful.

00:07:50.400 --> 00:07:52.880
So that for someone who is genuine but confused,

00:07:52.880 --> 00:07:55.760
which seems to be the characteristic of many seekers,

00:07:56.000 --> 00:08:02.899
certainly, I mean I would certainly describe myself as being confused

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:08.782
when I think about the state I was before I met Shri Mataji.

00:08:08.880 --> 00:08:13.872
It's very difficult to know who is genuine and who is not,

00:08:14.022 --> 00:08:14.880
who delivers the goods and who doesn't,

00:08:14.880 --> 00:08:20.622
and who is just a kind of illusion makers.

00:08:20.722 --> 00:08:30.541
So the way to go about this riddle is just to submit to you that

00:08:30.640 --> 00:08:34.960
whatever may be said on Sahaja Yoga is for you an hypothesis.

00:08:35.680 --> 00:08:38.720
And this is probably what Shri Mataji will tell you also in a few minutes.

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:48.939
Now you know that for an hypothesis to be considered as a law,

00:08:49.040 --> 00:08:51.440
it has to fulfill two requirements,

00:08:51.440 --> 00:08:56.000
it has to be communicable and verifiable under certain conditions.

00:08:56.560 --> 00:09:02.560
So the hypothesis of Sahaja Yoga which is going to be laid down or presented for you,

00:09:02.560 --> 00:09:05.920
is going to be verified for those who saw desire,

00:09:05.920 --> 00:09:07.360
not for the others of course,

00:09:08.080 --> 00:09:12.240
by a session of meditation at the end of the program of Shri Mataji,

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:17.920
in which Shri Mataji will again show her absolutely amazing capacity

00:09:19.280 --> 00:09:24.720
to play this catalytical role in granting people their self-realization.

00:09:25.600 --> 00:09:28.915
So if you came here to listen to a lecture,

00:09:29.280 --> 00:09:37.440
you are like someone who came and thought he had five dollars in his pocket,

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:39.840
but it's not five, it's five thousand dollars.

00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:46.400
Because really what you can get this evening is much more than analytical knowledge,

00:09:46.400 --> 00:09:48.880
which is communicated by means of words.

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:55.512
So this is a kind of introduction to the hypothesis.

00:09:56.640 --> 00:10:10.800
And I assure you that the only thing it takes to verify what is actually going on,

00:10:11.440 --> 00:10:19.625
is a certain intellectual honesty, that's all, a certain genuineness.

00:10:20.720 --> 00:10:23.760
And of course a desire to know what's going on,

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:27.840
not about Sahaja Yoga of course, but what's going on about our own life,

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:30.827
about the way to fulfill it.

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:38.320
Now the hypothesis is very simple, this is the framework of the hypothesis,

00:10:39.280 --> 00:10:44.281
and what we say is this,

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:51.040
you have the sacrum bone, which is more or less at the bottom of your spine,

00:10:51.680 --> 00:10:55.360
an energy which could be called in our tradition as

00:10:55.920 --> 00:11:02.480
the residual consciousness of the Holy Spirit in man.

00:11:04.640 --> 00:11:07.440
This energy is called Kundalini in Sanskrit.

00:11:09.200 --> 00:11:12.720
Now what we call Self-realization,

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:19.920
that has to be defined, is the following process.

00:11:19.920 --> 00:11:25.526
It's the process of this energy going up within the spine,

00:11:25.920 --> 00:11:31.440
crossing this famous point known as the third eye in various esoteric traditions,

00:11:32.720 --> 00:11:36.160
going through this beautiful flower here,

00:11:36.720 --> 00:11:44.720
which Lord Buddha described as the thousand petaled lotus,

00:11:45.360 --> 00:11:50.000
and oozing out of the top of the skull.

00:11:51.120 --> 00:11:56.960
Now when this takes place, what does it mean, what are the implications?

00:12:02.240 --> 00:12:05.370
I think Shri Mataji is already coming.

00:12:13.090 --> 00:12:16.230
What are the implications of this process?

00:12:17.920 --> 00:12:26.080
First of all you can register the process in, I would say, essentially two ways.

00:12:29.120 --> 00:12:34.960
When the energy crosses this center, the Agnya chakra,

00:12:35.760 --> 00:12:40.320
one enters into a state which is a state of silence.

00:12:41.360 --> 00:12:45.920
Now we all know we'd rather think a lot and it's not easy to stop thinking,

00:12:45.920 --> 00:12:49.360
even if we do so, I mean if we wish to do so.

00:12:51.680 --> 00:13:01.200
This state of silence announces the quality of what Lord Jesus Christ has described as the

00:13:01.200 --> 00:13:06.160
kingdom of God, because when one can penetrate farther into this silence,

00:13:07.600 --> 00:13:17.040
one undoubtedly discovers a new quality of being, and I would like to come back on this.

00:13:17.600 --> 00:13:24.612
Now once the Kundalini is just a couple of centimeters upwards and oozes out of the head,

00:13:24.980 --> 00:13:28.020
then what happens?

00:13:27.920 --> 00:13:34.823
There again what happens has been referred to in very ancient texts,

00:13:35.520 --> 00:13:46.880
what actually happens is one feels the manifestation of something which is a cool breeze,

00:13:47.840 --> 00:13:58.944
and this is a cool breeze which was called as Pneuma Onus by the Greek Fathers of the Church.

00:14:00.640 --> 00:14:10.000
It was referred to also in the Bible as this mighty wind which erupted in the house

00:14:12.160 --> 00:14:15.120
where the apostles were gathered for Pentecost.

00:14:16.880 --> 00:14:22.800
There are many references in various cultures to this phenomenon that we call vibrations.

00:14:24.080 --> 00:14:29.680
What actually happens is that our central nervous system, which means this physical system by which

00:14:29.680 --> 00:14:35.680
we feel sensations, becomes aware of a subtle energy which was always existing before,

00:14:36.320 --> 00:14:42.160
but which we could not perceive. It's like you have let's say a radio here,

00:14:42.720 --> 00:14:48.240
I mean if the radio is not switched on it cannot pick up all the waves and the music which is in

00:14:48.240 --> 00:14:55.600
the room in the same way. Self-realization allows our central nervous system to pick on those waves,

00:14:55.600 --> 00:15:04.480
to feel these vibrations which are a spiritual energy. In other words, this is the meeting point

00:15:04.480 --> 00:15:13.440
of matter and spirit because with the material structure one becomes aware of spirit, and this

00:15:13.440 --> 00:15:23.440
is a breakthrough into the fourth dimension. These vibrations are the category of perception that Kant

00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:32.240
was requiring in order to know the things in themselves, in order to know reality,

00:15:32.880 --> 00:15:39.080
and it is because at that time he said that we don't have this new or this other category

00:15:39.170 --> 00:15:44.530
of perception to know metaphysical realities, metaphysics, that is what is beyond physics.

00:15:44.720 --> 00:15:50.860
That is why we should just limit ourselves to rationality and from there on the whole

00:15:51.310 --> 00:15:58.910
demach, the whole direction of the western seekers went into basically this finite world

00:15:59.440 --> 00:16:04.240
and no more this world which was keeping people like Plato and Socrates busy,

00:16:04.240 --> 00:16:11.200
the world of the things in themselves, of reality. Now this is important to know because this

00:16:11.200 --> 00:16:16.960
breakthrough in our category of perception has been solved by so many seekers that people who

00:16:16.960 --> 00:16:23.680
know that background, would it be only intellectually, know that one thing has to happen

00:16:24.640 --> 00:16:31.440
in order to know reality, is that we have to have a new means and this is how you'll better

00:16:31.440 --> 00:16:36.640
understand the importance of these vibrations and the importance of what can be done with them.

00:16:37.680 --> 00:16:44.400
This is such a rich and vast topic that I simply would not like to enter into it now.

00:16:45.120 --> 00:16:52.320
Now going back to what I said a few minutes ago, this quality of silence one discovers at the level

00:16:52.320 --> 00:17:01.520
of the Agnya chakra is the space of reality between two thought movements. Now the action

00:17:01.520 --> 00:17:08.240
of this energy which we have called Kundalini pushes the thoughts on the side and then you

00:17:08.240 --> 00:17:17.600
enter in your own realm. What actually happened is this, is that once that the Kundalini is at the

00:17:17.600 --> 00:17:28.560
top of the head there is a secret link between the head and the heart and the heart is the seat

00:17:28.560 --> 00:17:38.240
of the self, the spirit, the Atma in Sanskrit. So through this link in your consciousness,

00:17:38.240 --> 00:17:45.920
in your brain you start imbibing Atma consciousness, that means you start being

00:17:45.920 --> 00:17:55.360
aware conscious of those qualities which are the qualities of the self which are called Sat-Chit-Ananda

00:17:56.160 --> 00:18:00.480
meaning truth consciousness and bliss.

00:18:05.680 --> 00:18:07.520
So this is the hypothesis

00:18:10.240 --> 00:18:13.330
as shortly as I could [say].

00:18:21.180 --> 00:18:24.810
This is true Shri Mataji.

00:19:05.675 --> 00:19:09.870
As I mentioned

00:19:09.920 --> 00:19:17.520
the very reassuring thing about Sahaja Yoga is that nobody is ever taught to believe in anything that

00:19:18.160 --> 00:19:22.080
is not object of experience and perception.

00:19:27.520 --> 00:19:35.040
I also mentioned that for those who saw desire the verification of the hypothesis can take place

00:19:35.040 --> 00:19:45.443
at the end of this program. Now I should perhaps before ending tell you why it is so.

00:19:45.823 --> 00:19:51.520
Why it is that we who are very, I should say normal people, why is it that we should be in

00:19:51.520 --> 00:20:01.392
a position to know this experience? What have we done to deserve it? I mean if I ask this question

00:20:01.592 --> 00:20:08.662
for myself I'm a bit puzzled because I certainly did not at any point have the

00:20:08.752 --> 00:20:15.428
got the feeling that I had done anything to deserve that.

00:20:15.578 --> 00:20:19.360
So it came as such a surprise to me that I should get my realization that really for

00:20:19.360 --> 00:20:28.430
quite some time I would not quite believe that it is so. And I found out later on that many people

00:20:28.470 --> 00:20:33.985
have the same difficulty to relate to something which is so incredibly beyond our wildest dream

00:20:34.075 --> 00:20:38.825
that it's just too good to be true. You know where is the catch? I mean it's not possible.

00:20:38.915 --> 00:20:43.760
Well it is. And Shri Mataji is as a very which I welcome here, very gracious of you to have come and

00:20:44.320 --> 00:20:53.165
we thank you so much. We certainly are very grateful to you for coming Shri Mataji.

00:20:53.280 --> 00:20:58.880
Shri Mataji is a very poetical simple image which in my view is perfect for the world.

00:20:59.040 --> 00:21:04.640
Which in my view is perfect because it carries the strength of simplicity and it says it all.

00:21:04.640 --> 00:21:10.240
Shri Mataji says that well if you have a tree which starts producing flowers in the middle of

00:21:10.240 --> 00:21:19.760
winter under snow and storm this is a miracle. And that miracle where those great souls of the past

00:21:19.760 --> 00:21:26.400
which received their realization at a point where the whole evolutionary process was not quite

00:21:26.400 --> 00:21:31.360
mature for this. Therefore they had to struggle in an incredible way. And this is what you learn

00:21:31.360 --> 00:21:41.840
when you study the lives of such great people. Now if this same tree is blossoming in spring it's

00:21:41.840 --> 00:21:52.480
not a miracle. It's nature's ways and rhythm. It is the dance of evolution. It is the moment that

00:21:52.480 --> 00:22:01.040
should happen. And so Shri Mataji says we now have entered the time where this process of triggering

00:22:01.600 --> 00:22:10.400
en masse self-realization has come. And if you study arts, literature, anything, any parameter

00:22:10.400 --> 00:22:14.800
of modern civilization you know that there is a tremendous expectation for this kind of

00:22:14.800 --> 00:22:22.480
breakthrough. And this is pretty obvious that today Englishmen for instance are not motivated

00:22:22.480 --> 00:22:28.640
by many things certainly not by competing with Japanese in order to make gadgets. I mean the

00:22:28.640 --> 00:22:38.560
economic indicators prove that they don't devote much energy to these things. So what do they care about?

00:22:38.560 --> 00:22:50.160
Cricket maybe but other things too. And actually I would submit that it is probably an evolutionary

00:22:50.160 --> 00:22:55.440
progress to accept that GNP should decrease because one does not bother about it. But then

00:22:55.440 --> 00:23:02.000
what should we devote our attention to? And many people in this country as in any so-called

00:23:02.000 --> 00:23:06.960
industrial countries are trying to devote more energy to the pursuit of this inner truth.

00:23:07.920 --> 00:23:14.880
The only trouble is the setup that I've described before is that there is such a big show in town

00:23:14.880 --> 00:23:21.440
that people don't go into the right shop because first of all they assume it has to be found in a

00:23:21.440 --> 00:23:34.320
shop where you can buy it and this is the first mistake. So here you can't buy because it's too

00:23:34.320 --> 00:23:42.640
expensive. It's so expensive that it can only be given. Shri Mataji says that realization is

00:23:42.640 --> 00:23:48.880
as important as breathing. If you would have to puncture your bank account in order to have

00:23:48.880 --> 00:23:53.520
the right to breathe you would be dead long time back. And this it is the same thing.

00:23:56.800 --> 00:24:03.440
So it happens now because now the time has come and it happens for another reason. And this

00:24:03.440 --> 00:24:06.800
other reason if I may say so is sitting before you.

00:24:09.680 --> 00:24:22.080
Now speaking to I would say a few people who have never had exposure to Sahaja Yoga,

00:24:22.080 --> 00:24:26.880
I should certainly keep a kind of sobriety while introducing Shri Mataji which is difficult

00:24:27.680 --> 00:24:36.320
because her achievements are so extraordinary that they are difficult to express in English

00:24:36.320 --> 00:24:41.295
which is a language appreciating understatements.

00:24:43.120 --> 00:24:48.960
It's very difficult to understate Shri Mataji. I mean we are condemned to understate her anyway

00:24:49.760 --> 00:24:59.200
but how to give some or render some justice to her labor, the work she has been doing in this

00:24:59.200 --> 00:25:04.320
country and I should say in the whole of Western Europe not to mention Australia and of course

00:25:04.320 --> 00:25:14.320
India. What I know is that she's a totally selfless, totally genuine person. Not only

00:25:14.320 --> 00:25:21.120
she didn't ever take any penny, I should blush for saying such a nonsense from anybody,

00:25:21.760 --> 00:25:29.520
but the first lot of her followers in London were of such a kind of economically derelict

00:25:29.520 --> 00:25:35.600
soul that she had to pay for the rent of the flat for some time. So this is one of the oddities of

00:25:35.600 --> 00:25:41.440
Sahaja Yoga and there are many others that you will discover in your time. Shri Mataji

00:25:42.000 --> 00:25:49.840
despite a tremendous power that we would not be able to face if that power would not be just

00:25:51.280 --> 00:26:01.360
love, despite siddhis, despite qualities that in my humble view are to be found in nobody on this

00:26:01.360 --> 00:26:06.480
earth and I have seen a lot of so-called spiritual people before I met Shri Mataji. Despite all this

00:26:07.280 --> 00:26:19.438
she's extremely human, I mean much more than me, I'm quite surprised about that.

00:26:24.000 --> 00:26:32.720
There is a word in Sanskrit for this and this word is called Mahamaya and Mahamaya means the

00:26:32.720 --> 00:26:37.920
great illusion. So you have the privilege to sit this evening in front of

00:26:39.360 --> 00:26:46.590
a very very great illusion and this is the illusion that you're in front of a human being.

00:26:48.400 --> 00:26:52.960
It's a nice illusion though because if you would realize that it is not so,

00:26:53.520 --> 00:26:56.000
you may run away and this is not the purpose of the evening.

00:27:07.672 --> 00:27:14.432
So I suppose that I should end this few words by means of introduction.

00:27:15.440 --> 00:27:25.920
Thanking you very much for having come all the way from wherever you came and if Sahaja Yoga

00:27:26.800 --> 00:27:30.000
is full of joy, is full of humor, it's also a sacred reality.

00:27:31.360 --> 00:27:39.120
It is the sacred reality of our innermost divine being

00:27:39.840 --> 00:27:49.040
which opens itself if we in all humility and sincerity so wish. Shri Mataji, I am again

00:27:49.040 --> 00:27:55.200
in the name of everybody most graceful that you should grace this evening and it is my

00:27:55.200 --> 00:28:01.360
humblest prayer that everybody who has come should experience their Self-realization and what is even

00:28:02.240 --> 00:28:09.280
I should say what is even as important as that should understand what great great gift

00:28:14.959 --> 00:28:23.280
that evening is for them. Thank you very much.

00:28:30.268 --> 00:28:32.768
It's beautiful flowers.

00:29:11.257 --> 00:29:14.107
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

