00:29:34.720 --> 00:29:49.120
Brown, hopes against hopes, and they spent lot of money for this program and I only feel

00:29:49.120 --> 00:29:58.160
sorry that every time they have a public program we get very few people and even if you get

00:29:58.210 --> 00:30:04.730
Last time we had about three hundred people who were new. They got, some of them did touch

00:30:04.780 --> 00:30:15.580
realization. They looked very serious but nothing inside. We lost most of them because

00:30:15.600 --> 00:30:25.600
you see we have become used to our mental capacity to enact something and not to be

00:30:25.840 --> 00:30:33.840
the reality. It's a speciality of mental people that they talk too much, they say too

00:30:33.840 --> 00:30:44.480
much, have nothing with them. It's very shocking sometimes when you see how people

00:30:44.480 --> 00:30:53.520
say things about reality. I watch sometimes television, I see people on the television

00:30:53.760 --> 00:31:00.080
and I feel they are somewhere near reality, they are talking about reality. They understand

00:31:00.080 --> 00:31:08.240
that there's something missing in their lives and they are looking for it but when

00:31:08.240 --> 00:31:17.360
it comes to actualization and to achieving what you have, whatever is your own, they

00:31:17.920 --> 00:31:27.920
become absolutely mundane, frivolous, very surprising. I can't understand why it should

00:31:27.920 --> 00:31:35.920
happen. Now supposing you say, as Gregoire has been giving Me certificates, great certificates

00:31:35.920 --> 00:31:41.920
he has given and also he's a diplomat so diplomatically he was trying to please all

00:31:41.920 --> 00:31:48.240
of you so that you take to Sahaja Yoga because he doesn't want you to commit the same mistakes

00:31:48.240 --> 00:32:01.600
that most of them have committed. But despite all that let us face ourselves clearly. Newcomers

00:32:01.600 --> 00:32:09.600
are absolutely a minority here so I'm talking also to Sahaja Yogis. Let us face ourselves

00:32:09.600 --> 00:32:20.720
fully. Are we ourselves? We've got everything supposing, we say, All right, we have seen

00:32:20.720 --> 00:32:28.400
the power of political achievement, of economic achievements, of other achievements which

00:32:28.400 --> 00:32:36.640
we call emotional achievements. But have we really faced ourselves? Have we seen ourselves?

00:32:36.640 --> 00:32:46.480
What is our quality of life? I asked an Englishman, I said, What is the quality of an Englishman?

00:32:46.480 --> 00:32:54.880
He said, It depends on how many times he goes for a sea resort. Can you imagine? What? Sea

00:32:54.880 --> 00:33:01.040
resort. How many years back did you start going to the sea resort? I don't think we

00:33:01.040 --> 00:33:05.840
never heard about it in India. It's about twenty-five years back, somebody's stupid

00:33:05.840 --> 00:33:12.640
fellow must be, or somebody very clever maybe, put this idea that we all should go to the

00:33:12.640 --> 00:33:24.560
sea resort because we must get our skin full of cancer. So the quality of a person doesn't

00:33:24.560 --> 00:33:37.120
depend on a mental acceptance of something that looks new. And that's what is happening

00:33:37.120 --> 00:33:44.560
to all of us is, anything new that comes, we accept it and we think we have equality.

00:33:44.560 --> 00:33:51.520
If a lady goes supposing to us at a sea resort, because I meet the other kind also who are

00:33:51.520 --> 00:33:58.320
not seekers at all, she'll come and tell and say, Now see what tan I have got. I mean,

00:33:58.320 --> 00:34:06.320
it's so superficial, it's so frivolous, it's so nonsensical. I mean, is this the

00:34:06.320 --> 00:34:15.920
value of your life? You have come out of amoeba stage to this stage and what are you doing

00:34:15.920 --> 00:34:27.760
about yourself, making it tan? That sometimes really makes me feel very disappointed. And

00:34:27.760 --> 00:34:39.760
this is such a common topic all over. What are we? We are human beings. We have come

00:34:39.760 --> 00:34:47.200
out of amoeba to other stage and other stage in thousands of years. Today we are human

00:34:47.200 --> 00:35:00.880
beings, made to achieve something great. Nature has worked on us relentlessly, so beautifully,

00:35:00.880 --> 00:35:12.880
so delicately, so lovingly, for what? And when we just become mental, according to Indian

00:35:12.880 --> 00:35:21.280
philosophers, a mental person is nothing but a stupid fellow. Egoistical person he becomes

00:35:21.280 --> 00:35:29.280
and he becomes nothing but a stupid fellow. Because anything that comes of the mental

00:35:29.280 --> 00:35:37.680
expression. Today I was only watching about the modern art. Modern art is all right if

00:35:37.680 --> 00:35:48.320
you know how to become super modern, that is a realized soul. But this modern art was

00:35:48.320 --> 00:35:56.320
described by a gentleman and then ultimately he got into the real mood of saying something

00:35:56.320 --> 00:36:02.720
that is the truth. He said that this all expression shows that we were barbaric and

00:36:02.720 --> 00:36:18.800
now we have become worse than barbaric. So the whole expression of our life is something

00:36:18.800 --> 00:36:27.520
that we have done out of our mental thing, we are so much in imbalance. Now the main

00:36:27.520 --> 00:36:38.320
thing one has to understand that you are made a human being by the kindness, the grace of

00:36:38.320 --> 00:36:54.640
the nature of God Almighty, as I call it. Not by you, not by mental thought. You have

00:36:54.640 --> 00:37:07.440
a special value, you have a very, very special value in the eyes of the nature, in the working

00:37:07.440 --> 00:37:20.560
of the evolutionary process. Have we got any concept as to what is expected out of

00:37:20.560 --> 00:37:37.360
us? Are we to waste our life into these frivolous, stupid things, doing everything very simply

00:37:37.360 --> 00:37:44.160
seriously though? They're very serious about all stupidity, especially then they

00:37:44.160 --> 00:37:48.720
talk for a greater stupidity they are more serious. They think without that there won't

00:37:48.720 --> 00:37:58.960
be any impression on people. But the main thing is we have missed the point. The point

00:37:58.960 --> 00:38:08.400
is you have to be the Spirit. All these doings are to be the Spirit. It's not talking,

00:38:08.400 --> 00:38:13.120
it's not your mental projections, all your new ideas coming up and going up, it's not

00:38:13.120 --> 00:38:27.200
that. It is you have to be the Spirit. Face it up. This you cannot purchase in the market,

00:38:27.200 --> 00:38:36.240
you cannot. You cannot put in any effort. Now you are that, just to become that. That's

00:38:36.240 --> 00:38:50.560
what your quality is. That's what I see you as. Or anybody who is a realized soul.

00:38:50.560 --> 00:38:59.549
But what do you see yourself as, is the main point. That's why there cannot be much report.

00:39:06.480 --> 00:39:13.280
Anything new that is brought to you, oh it's nice. How, how do you know?

00:39:15.040 --> 00:39:19.440
Traditions we have put on one side, because tradition means all conditioning,

00:39:20.320 --> 00:39:27.520
all wrong things, tradition we don't want, all right. So now what are you clinging to?

00:39:28.240 --> 00:39:34.560
At least tradition had one safe point. That trial and error you have found out something sensible.

00:39:35.200 --> 00:39:43.120
Now you put tradition all nonsense. Why? Because you cannot take out the good out of that tradition.

00:39:43.680 --> 00:39:50.080
So now you are going to the other side saying, all right, no tradition, we love this new style.

00:39:50.720 --> 00:40:00.640
We don't want to be covered by any tradition. Like people might say, what is in a painting of say,

00:40:00.880 --> 00:40:13.360
of say, Marlowe, whom I like very much, say, what is so great? We can do some drip painting.

00:40:13.360 --> 00:40:17.760
They have drip painting, I don't know what sort of paintings they have these days.

00:40:17.760 --> 00:40:21.440
Why should we? You can't do even one painting like that.

00:40:21.440 --> 00:40:34.046
You can't even reproduce. You cannot think of such a painting, face it. Modern mind is incapable

00:40:34.156 --> 00:40:50.094
of conceiving that. Accept it. You have gone down in quality. Why? Because of mental movement.

00:40:50.244 --> 00:40:59.259
It's such a limited movement, but those people believed in something higher, higher, higher

00:40:59.399 --> 00:41:10.059
ideals. They thought of God, they thought of perfecting themselves, not putting the chaos in

00:41:10.139 --> 00:41:20.895
your heart outside, no, perfecting, resting in that, believing in that, in that peaceful

00:41:21.005 --> 00:41:26.345
atmosphere they created something that you cannot produce. Only thing what you can do?

00:41:26.415 --> 00:41:34.814
I don't like it. Like in my house, I was screen made in Saranpur long time back, it's beautifully

00:41:34.874 --> 00:41:40.854
done, it has got beautiful honeycomb work which no one can do. Found some people came

00:41:40.904 --> 00:41:52.869
to see, I don't like it. I said, can you make even three inches of that? That's the only

00:41:52.969 --> 00:41:59.520
thing you can do is to say, I don't like it, finished. Can you do three inches? Can you?

00:42:00.080 --> 00:42:09.040
You can't. Accept this fact. Once you accept this fact, I'm sure the humility that is needed

00:42:09.040 --> 00:42:18.560
will come into you. Humility is lacking. Seekers must have humility, otherwise they will go

00:42:18.560 --> 00:42:23.040
to people who will pamper their egos and they will be drifted into nonsensical till their

00:42:23.120 --> 00:42:30.400
money is finished, till they become absolutely lunatics or epileptics, they will just continue

00:42:30.400 --> 00:42:42.480
and will finish off. But to be sensible, to be sane, one has to understand that our worth

00:42:42.480 --> 00:42:48.320
is much more than this. Like a BBC fellow comes and tells Me, I mean he thinks, he's

00:42:48.320 --> 00:42:53.200
praising you, I don't know what, whatever you may call it, that an Anglo-Saxon brain

00:42:53.200 --> 00:43:01.440
cannot understand anything spiritual for which you don't have to pay. I really tell you

00:43:01.440 --> 00:43:07.680
that he said it to Me. And I refused to go on that BBC because I said, first of all,

00:43:07.680 --> 00:43:13.440
your Anglo-Saxon brain must be all right. Is it a special brain you have made, Anglo-Saxon

00:43:13.440 --> 00:43:23.680
brains, are they specially made by God? When you say you are Anglo-Saxon brain you have

00:43:23.680 --> 00:43:32.960
absolutely put down your value, down. And when you say it's a human brain, then you

00:43:32.960 --> 00:43:43.520
are great because you become one of that great world. There's no global sense, we

00:43:43.520 --> 00:43:50.000
don't have a global sense at all within ourselves. Whatever we have is so localized

00:43:50.000 --> 00:44:01.120
and insular understanding, so insular that we just say, I don't like it, I don't

00:44:01.120 --> 00:44:14.400
want it. Who is this I, is only possible when we come to some humility.

00:44:14.400 --> 00:44:20.560
With all respect to England, because England to Me is very great and it's the heart of

00:44:20.560 --> 00:44:25.760
the universe. And when I say this in the European countries they get rather upset, Mother, what?

00:44:25.760 --> 00:44:32.160
England is the heart, that's too much, Mother, we can't digest this. It is the

00:44:32.160 --> 00:44:46.640
heart, whatever you like it or not. It is the heart, no doubt. But what a heart, can't

00:44:46.640 --> 00:45:02.240
break it, you know, cannot make it expand. This is the sad part of English, is, it's

00:45:02.240 --> 00:45:13.440
the heart, is a very important organ of the universe. But the cells that exist here, who

00:45:13.440 --> 00:45:21.440
are supposed to circulate in the whole world, who have to achieve so many things as the

00:45:21.440 --> 00:45:38.640
cells of the heart achieve by pumping out new refreshed blood, is expected to have beautiful

00:45:38.640 --> 00:45:49.440
heart, an English mark, a heart that is to be cherished, to be enjoyed and appreciated.

00:45:49.440 --> 00:46:02.000
Where are they? With all this expenditure on these people here, previously I used to

00:46:02.000 --> 00:46:08.480
do it in England, but I gave up, exhausted all my bank and how many disciples I get are

00:46:08.480 --> 00:46:16.160
seven for four years. I said, give up these people, good for nothing, useless. All the

00:46:16.160 --> 00:46:23.840
money they spend, and what do you find, what's the quality, how many come up and how many

00:46:23.840 --> 00:46:38.400
work it out, how many care for their Self-realization? For Me to say that I work very hard, I don't

00:46:38.400 --> 00:46:51.440
think I work at all, I don't work. I do not work, it emits, it's there. But it's

00:46:51.440 --> 00:47:09.440
a waste, it's a waste land. How are we going to sow the seed in the waste land? How

00:47:09.440 --> 00:47:18.720
are we going to work it out? Especially London seems to be a rock, rock of Gibraltar has

00:47:18.720 --> 00:47:24.400
come in London, I think. For this place, Wimbledon, you'll be surprised, we are very

00:47:24.400 --> 00:47:31.760
fond of tennis, so both of us used to come. And our driver would say, we must go one hour

00:47:31.760 --> 00:47:40.800
earlier. Why? You just can't get in there. And we used to come one hour earlier to get

00:47:40.800 --> 00:47:50.240
into the lanes of this Wimbledon to go and see the tennis. And the same Wimbledon has

00:47:50.240 --> 00:47:56.880
twenty people, new people over here. I really wanted to go back, because I felt what sort

00:47:56.880 --> 00:48:03.680
of a quality is this that I'm wasting my time with. We tried everything, diplomatic

00:48:03.680 --> 00:48:11.280
relationship, food we invited them, gave them food, tea, Indian tea, all kinds of things

00:48:11.280 --> 00:48:23.760
we tried, that a mother should try her level best. You don't understand this. Of course

00:48:23.760 --> 00:48:29.680
the Indians who are here are all uprooted people, I don't call them Indians at all,

00:48:29.680 --> 00:48:35.360
most of them. They are just uprooted people. They don't understand the value of their

00:48:35.360 --> 00:48:44.240
life, no, most of them. Of course there are some sensible people also, no doubt, a very

00:48:44.240 --> 00:48:50.800
few. So now what are we to do, supposing there is something great that has to happen to this

00:48:50.800 --> 00:48:56.480
world, and that you are the ones who have to be blessed. You can you believe it? I've

00:48:56.480 --> 00:49:07.680
been here for twelve years now, this will be the twelfth year. But there's a guru who

00:49:07.680 --> 00:49:15.120
wants a Rolls Royce, he's already got fifty-eight, he wants a fifty-ninth. There are sixty thousand

00:49:15.120 --> 00:49:25.600
people here who are buying a Rolls Royce for that person. What happens to your brains,

00:49:25.600 --> 00:49:36.320
I can't understand. Is that the Spirit? Is that what you are seeking? Understatement

00:49:36.320 --> 00:49:46.720
I understand, but undervaluing I don't understand. No value for your own being, not for your

00:49:46.720 --> 00:50:02.560
own evolution and for your own personality. I tell you, I've done everything under the

00:50:02.560 --> 00:50:08.880
sun in this country. In India I've hardly worked for two years, and we have thousands

00:50:08.880 --> 00:50:13.920
and thousands of people who are Sahaja Yogis today. Our country is going to change very

00:50:13.920 --> 00:50:29.520
fast, I know that. It will work out even in so many other countries. But England, William

00:50:29.520 --> 00:50:35.520
Blake, I don't know, he dreamt so great about England because he knew the quality

00:50:35.520 --> 00:50:48.640
of England, that Jerusalem. Do you think, you still hope what he said? You have such

00:50:48.640 --> 00:50:57.520
an advantage of your language, you have such an advantage that you can read about so many

00:50:57.520 --> 00:51:04.960
things. Most of the books of philosophy are translated into your language. You are specially

00:51:05.200 --> 00:51:20.320
being blessed by so much of knowledge, despite that. Why, why people are so much unaware

00:51:20.320 --> 00:51:36.880
of their worth, of their deserving capacity. What do they deserve? Let's see. Is the

00:51:36.880 --> 00:51:41.920
expectation of the disasters that are going to come, or horrible things that are going

00:51:41.920 --> 00:51:47.040
to happen in this world, all these things, do we deserve or do we deserve some sort of

00:51:47.040 --> 00:51:54.640
a great hope for ourselves? And everything is within you, you can see that, it's all

00:51:54.640 --> 00:52:04.000
there, it's your own. Why shouldn't you have it? I mean, we have tried everything

00:52:04.010 --> 00:52:09.259
to push you down to that point, every way, every method. As in Sanskrit they say,

00:52:09.309 --> 00:52:16.640
‘Kāma, Dama, Daṇḍa, Bheda, Nīti’, everything, five things we have tried, to work it out. So now only

00:52:16.640 --> 00:52:23.200
another thing is to push people with piston up there and keep them waiting. That also

00:52:23.200 --> 00:52:39.840
perhaps you've done, isn't it? The whole world is looking at you, remember that.

00:52:40.800 --> 00:52:49.120
Not big talking, not big saying, but the big thing happening within you, is actualization

00:52:49.120 --> 00:52:59.200
of that great thing, which is so simple, so beautiful. It takes hardly anything for you

00:52:59.200 --> 00:53:07.200
to become your Spirit, but to maintain it, to respect it and to be there. I don't know

00:53:07.440 --> 00:53:14.320
what sort of a special glue we should have, they just don't stick on. They meet Me on

00:53:14.320 --> 00:53:20.320
the shop, Mother, I said, how? Oh, you don't know, I came to it twelve years back, you

00:53:20.320 --> 00:53:25.440
gave Me realization, all right, now what are you doing about it? Mother, I lost it, you

00:53:25.440 --> 00:53:39.120
know, really. It's very common, very common phenomenon. So those who are here today, twenty

00:53:39.120 --> 00:53:53.040
people, I hope are special, and they consider this experience as something special, and

00:53:53.200 --> 00:54:02.880
establish themselves as great saints, knowing everything about their own powers.

00:54:06.160 --> 00:54:10.080
It all has to be free, you cannot pay for it.

00:54:15.280 --> 00:54:22.800
I'm really frustrated, I must say. I was going away this time to India, I would have been there,

00:54:23.040 --> 00:54:34.720
but as you say, one is more concerned about the lost lambs. India is very easy, so I've

00:54:34.720 --> 00:54:41.120
stuck back. I hope you are not going to disappoint Me, those who have come for the first time,

00:54:41.120 --> 00:54:50.560
please, Gregoire has tried his tricks, everybody tries, but I don't know how to make people

00:54:50.560 --> 00:54:58.160
stick. A surprising, in the West people have developed the best quality glues, we cannot

00:54:58.160 --> 00:55:04.480
develop such in India, or any developing countries, don't have glues, but as far as they are

00:55:04.480 --> 00:55:12.320
concerned they cannot stick on to anything whatsoever. They cannot stick on to their

00:55:12.320 --> 00:55:15.760
wives, they cannot stick on to their husbands, they cannot stick on to their houses, they

00:55:16.000 --> 00:55:22.640
cannot stick on to anything whatsoever. And whatever has to grow has to stick on somewhere.

00:55:26.080 --> 00:55:32.880
If you have to make a well, then you find some water, then you dig it down, then you dig one,

00:55:32.880 --> 00:55:36.880
then another, then another, then go about. That's not the way.

00:55:36.960 --> 00:55:47.920
There has to be that breaking into the depth that you are, there has to be that happening,

00:55:47.920 --> 00:55:57.920
where you break into your own depth, your own quality, your own wealth, but that time

00:55:57.920 --> 00:56:03.920
you don't give, you don't give to yourself, you have no time for yourself, you have time

00:56:04.160 --> 00:56:11.200
for all kinds of nonsensical things, but no time for yourself to see what beauty lies,

00:56:11.200 --> 00:56:27.280
what glory lies behind this body, above this mind, and below these emotions.

00:56:34.080 --> 00:56:43.680
I do not know any other method is possible now. I must say I give up, I've tried everything.

00:56:46.560 --> 00:56:52.640
And as you have heard about Sahaja Yoga, it's a fact, there's no doubt about it,

00:56:53.520 --> 00:56:59.280
there's nothing to lose, you are the Spirit, you have to become the Spirit.

00:56:59.600 --> 00:57:07.600
It must relate to the traditional expression of your evolution. It cannot cut out all the saints,

00:57:08.480 --> 00:57:18.173
all the great prophets, all the great religious leaders, it cannot cut out, but it integrates

00:57:18.240 --> 00:57:26.000
all the essences of these great advents who came on this earth to guide us. It does not cut out

00:57:26.880 --> 00:57:38.000
anywhere, and that's what is Sahaja Yoga. Sahaja, as you know, was spontaneous. Now,

00:57:39.040 --> 00:57:46.080
spontaneous can be quite misrepresented if you use through your brains. Spontaneous means

00:57:46.080 --> 00:57:52.320
it's a living process that should happen to all of you, and don't miss the point.

00:57:52.320 --> 00:58:06.032
You have to spend at least a month to see the light that you have got

00:58:06.560 --> 00:58:12.560
is to be carried much deeper into you. You are deep, you are great,

00:58:13.520 --> 00:58:19.920
but if you have to find the pearls that are hidden, you have to go deep down.

00:58:20.880 --> 00:58:28.160
It's very simple because the more you go deeper into yourself, the more you enjoy,

00:58:28.160 --> 00:58:38.640
the more you become a wholesome personality, a greater personality, a personality that sees

00:58:40.160 --> 00:58:46.480
everything on a universal level and understand everything that is global.

00:58:49.920 --> 00:59:01.520
I'm sorry today I am not in My real, proper mood, I should say,

00:59:03.760 --> 00:59:09.360
because I know how much these people have done. They have advertised, they have gone round,

00:59:11.040 --> 00:59:16.320
they have put up advertisements everywhere, put up so much money, you know, that what

00:59:16.320 --> 00:59:24.400
Standard Times or what, what was this, oh God, and that Times, also Times take so much

00:59:24.400 --> 00:59:31.200
money out of your pockets. Just think of it. They are like gurus, you see.

00:59:34.400 --> 00:59:40.960
All that to spend and what do you get out of it, one feels so sad, it's very sad.

00:59:41.200 --> 00:59:54.513
Of course America is so much worse that relatively you don't feel that sad when you think of America.

01:00:01.200 --> 01:00:08.800
But after describing all the American art today, the gentleman came to the conclusion

01:00:08.880 --> 01:00:16.880
and he said that after seeing all this art one reaches a conclusion to say that they

01:00:16.880 --> 01:00:25.440
were barbarians and now they have become worst barbarians. Oh God, I said, what am I to do

01:00:25.440 --> 01:00:32.080
with these Americans now? But to Me you are all My children, you are all Mine. I cannot

01:00:32.080 --> 01:00:38.960
allow you to be drifted away. Till the last I'll try to work out. I know I feel sometimes

01:00:38.960 --> 01:00:48.400
very desperate and sad. English have very much changed now. They are so much influenced

01:00:48.400 --> 01:00:54.800
by the French. Now the French are better but they are influenced by the old French and

01:00:54.880 --> 01:01:04.880
the old Americans, not the new ones. New ones are very alert. So all the old ideas of these

01:01:06.080 --> 01:01:13.760
nonsensical writers are lingering now in England, deposited like in a case of angina in the

01:01:13.840 --> 01:01:23.840
heart, you see, when there is hardening of the arteries, all the bad blood stagnates

01:01:23.840 --> 01:01:29.840
like that, it's happening, I feel. They have given up these ideas, they have rid of it,

01:01:29.840 --> 01:01:35.840
they don't want to have it. We are still continuing with them.

