Something respectable for ourselves, that's what I feel. Today being most of them, Sahaja

01:01:47.840 --> 01:01:53.840
Yogi is here, I'm sure you'll all get your realization in no time, I'm sure of that.

01:01:53.840 --> 01:02:00.840
But that's not sufficient. Out of the three hundred we got in Hampstead, with all the

01:02:00.840 --> 01:02:07.840
work these people did, advertising, this, that, whatever was possible, five people,

01:02:07.840 --> 01:02:18.840
some or other, stuck on, and only three I think with a great glue came down. That should

01:02:18.840 --> 01:02:24.840
not happen again. So specially for the new people I have to tell you that this is something

01:02:24.840 --> 01:02:33.840
so important that has come to be emboldened. All these tennis players, I've seen them

01:02:33.840 --> 01:02:39.840
coming and going. One comes this year, next year he goes away, somebody is today a top

01:02:39.840 --> 01:02:48.840
seat, then he goes down, not in Sahaja Yoga. You ascend and ascend and ascend and ascend,

01:02:48.840 --> 01:03:04.840
eternally. It's a very different style of tennis. It's a real plague. It's no professionals

01:03:04.840 --> 01:03:16.840
are needed, you become such tremendous players, such a game you develop. And that's what

01:03:16.840 --> 01:03:25.840
is there for you just to jump into it and to understand the swimming. And I'm sure

01:03:25.840 --> 01:03:34.840
it will work out. I hope all those who have come for the first time will not treat themselves

01:03:34.840 --> 01:03:44.840
frivolously, but will stand up to it and give us some encouragement to work out more in

01:03:44.840 --> 01:03:51.840
England. Otherwise maybe tomorrow all the Sahaja Yogis from here may come to India with

01:03:51.840 --> 01:03:59.840
their, what do you say, stock, what, stock, lock, lock, stock and barrel, lock, stock

01:03:59.840 --> 01:04:04.840
and barrel, of course without the barrels.

01:04:04.840 --> 01:04:12.840
Let's see now how it works out. There's nothing serious about it. You have to be

01:04:12.840 --> 01:04:19.840
very pleasantly placed towards yourself. This is one thing you should know. A person who

01:04:19.840 --> 01:04:35.840
is godly is never serious inside. He's playing the game. So in that playful mood of a Maldan,

01:04:35.840 --> 01:04:42.840
let us see what happens. May God bless you.

01:04:42.840 --> 01:04:49.840
Any questions? I'll have some water.

01:04:49.840 --> 01:04:51.840
Thank you.

