01:06:00.840 --> 01:06:08.840
Very much. But if you are a Christian, please be seated, please be seated.

01:06:08.840 --> 01:06:16.840
Christian is all right, any religion is all right, it's all great, but it has talked of the future.

01:06:16.840 --> 01:06:31.840
Christ has said, I will send you a comforter, counselor and a redeemer. Why don't the Christians

01:06:31.840 --> 01:06:41.840
look for someone like that? Christ is gone now, he's not here. Why don't they look out for

01:06:41.840 --> 01:06:45.723
a Holy Ghost?

01:06:56.840 --> 01:07:03.840
He himself has said it. Mohammed Sahib has said that during the time of resurrection

01:07:03.840 --> 01:07:18.840
your hands will speak. What about the Muslims? Why don't they look out for the resurrection?

01:07:18.840 --> 01:07:31.840
Third is Guru Nanaka, Kabira. Nanaka was so great that he combined all the realized souls

01:07:31.840 --> 01:07:46.788
who were poets and made a big beautiful grands-aub. What are the Sikhs doing? They are just reading it, reading it.

01:07:49.068 --> 01:08:00.840
He says, without knowing yourself you will be in illusion. He said very clearly. Then

01:08:00.840 --> 01:08:07.840
should we not look for that? But what happens, I tell you, what's the mistake is, once a

01:08:07.840 --> 01:08:20.840
religion is organized it neutralizes all your ascent. Organized. I also took My birth in

01:08:20.840 --> 01:08:33.840
the Christian religion, so-called I would say, specially that too Protestant for particular

01:08:33.840 --> 01:08:45.840
reasons. I could have taken birth anywhere else but now. And there is no talk of ascent,

01:08:45.840 --> 01:08:54.840
no talk of second birth. Artificially somebody puts his hand on your head, now you are a

01:08:54.840 --> 01:09:02.840
Christian. I don't know how you become. Same about Hindus, same about every one of them,

01:09:02.840 --> 01:09:13.840
they are leading an artificial religion. It's a garb. Reality is within. Whatever these

01:09:13.840 --> 01:09:23.840
people have worked and said is not done by them. It's become a superficial thing. You

01:09:23.840 --> 01:09:32.840
will not be happy unless and until you find your Spirit. How can you organize religion?

01:09:32.840 --> 01:09:45.840
How can you organize God? Then you think you belong to a church, you belong to a, what

01:09:45.840 --> 01:09:54.840
you call that, a sect or what is it called, another thing, something. Denomination. All

01:09:54.840 --> 01:10:03.840
these denominations brand us. What's the thing for me? All of them are just the same,

01:10:03.840 --> 01:10:18.840
still groping in the dark. How many are seeking reality? It's not that Christianity has failed,

01:10:18.840 --> 01:10:34.840
it is the church that has failed. Christ can never fail, nor can Guru Nanaka, nor can

01:10:34.840 --> 01:10:43.840
Mohammed Sahab. What fails is our understanding of them. Let us be the Spirit and then we'll

01:10:43.840 --> 01:10:51.840
understand them. They are all one, hand in hand, no difference at all. They are all one,

01:10:51.840 --> 01:11:07.840
believe Me. You don't have to give up anything, you have to just see to the essence of it.

01:11:07.840 --> 01:11:14.840
Supposing a leaf is sick, you cannot treat it at the leaf end, you have to go to the

01:11:14.840 --> 01:11:20.840
roots and when you go to the roots you find you have not given up any leaf. You are at

01:11:20.840 --> 01:11:26.840
the roots and you are at the leaf also everywhere you exist. There are so many seekers lost

01:11:26.840 --> 01:11:38.840
in this kind of a denomination, so many of them. Thank God my parents were realized souls,

01:11:38.840 --> 01:11:47.840
thank God, because I found Protestants with different type of fanatics, you see, very

01:11:47.840 --> 01:11:53.840
sophisticated. They would never find out that they are fanatics, so sophisticated, you know.

01:11:53.840 --> 01:12:00.840
If you make anything very sophisticated you can't find it out. We can call everybody

01:12:00.840 --> 01:12:06.840
else a fanatic but a Protestant you can never call because they are a mental people. They

01:12:06.840 --> 01:12:15.840
have made it very sophisticated. So if you become so very sophisticated that you cannot

01:12:15.840 --> 01:12:26.840
see yourself and you cannot make it out that it's I who is following some sort of a fanaticism,

01:12:26.840 --> 01:12:35.840
an ideology, a mental projection, how can you get out of it? From every religion people

01:12:35.840 --> 01:12:44.840
will think, oh Baba, this is fanaticism, this is too much. But for this I may be the most

01:12:44.840 --> 01:12:57.840
I may be the first and I hope I'm not the last. Martin Luther himself was a realized

01:12:57.840 --> 01:13:10.840
soul no doubt, but at that time, in that short time, with all kinds of oppressions and pressures,

01:13:10.840 --> 01:13:22.840
how far could he go? And then there's already an attack built in with Paul and then with

01:13:22.840 --> 01:13:34.840
Augustine. What can he do? Any realized soul like Khalil Gibran could see it clearly.

01:13:40.872 --> 01:13:50.840
So we have to know one thing, we have to love the truth. Truth is to be discovered through

01:13:50.840 --> 01:14:10.840
your Spirit and love your truth and not untruth. Any denomination is untruth. What is the truth?

01:14:11.840 --> 01:14:21.840
Is the essence of that. Everything is becoming a plastic and then we say why people are living

01:14:21.840 --> 01:14:27.840
churches, why people are running up from Christian faith or from that faith. Nothing wrong with

01:14:27.840 --> 01:14:36.840
Christ, I think. No, it's wrong with us that we have made all these plastic things

01:14:36.840 --> 01:14:49.840
to cover His image. The greatest justice you can do to Christ is to get your realization.

01:14:52.840 --> 01:15:03.840
He was crucified for that, He came for that and He waits for that. So please get your

01:15:03.840 --> 01:15:16.840
realization first and then you will know what is Christ and how great He is. May God bless

01:15:16.840 --> 01:15:17.840
you.

01:15:17.840 --> 01:15:23.840
What else is there? Any other question? It's a good question because that problem faces

01:15:23.840 --> 01:15:37.840
everyone of you. Let's see. There could be denominations like communist, capitalist,

01:15:37.840 --> 01:15:51.840
east, feast, all sorts of things. There could be, any time. I don't know the latest. I

01:15:51.840 --> 01:16:04.840
think lost counts after anti-culturists. There's only one denomination of God is

01:16:04.840 --> 01:16:16.840
a realized soul, a yogi, one with God. That's the only one. There's no other denomination

01:16:16.840 --> 01:16:31.840
where all of them combine, Christ, Mohammed, Lao Tse, Socrates, Krishna, Rama, Nanaka,

01:16:31.840 --> 01:16:40.840
Kabira, all of them combine in that great family of divinity.

01:16:41.840 --> 01:16:56.840
All right, so should we have realization? I mean most of you have had. Is there any

01:16:56.840 --> 01:17:00.777
question you can ask? I'll be very happy.

