again. Born again. You cannot call yourself anything. You see, it's a power, it's a state,

01:18:27.840 --> 01:18:31.840
it's a situation in which you have to be. If you are just born again, you say yourself,

01:18:31.840 --> 01:18:38.840
what is your power? Born again, the first power you get is that you become, your nerves

01:18:38.840 --> 01:18:50.840
become, your brain becomes collectively conscious in your awareness. That's the minimum that

01:18:50.840 --> 01:18:59.840
should happen to you. It's not certificate, it's another, oh I, that is the latest than

01:18:59.840 --> 01:19:11.840
the anti-culture is, then they might be the latest, is another denomination. Is no reality

01:19:11.840 --> 01:19:18.840
then. You don't know one of the, one of the, they attacked Me in Switzerland and the lady

01:19:18.840 --> 01:19:24.840
born again was wearing all kinds of glittery things and she was bringing a Bible to hit

01:19:24.840 --> 01:19:32.840
Me, you know, and I couldn't bear the whole joke and I started laughing and everybody

01:19:32.840 --> 01:19:36.840
was very upset but I was just laughing. I said, what a nice thing, born again coming

01:19:36.840 --> 01:19:45.840
up to hit Me. What wrong am I doing to you? But you see, the thing is the organized religion

01:19:45.840 --> 01:19:53.720
is such a possession, is such a security for people that they say, oh we are born again,

01:19:53.840 --> 01:20:02.720
now certified, certified and they feel very secured with it I think, otherwise I can't

01:20:02.840 --> 01:20:09.840
understand why should you accept such a title, you are born again, unless and until you have

01:20:09.840 --> 01:20:14.840
the power, you must know what is the power one should have as a born again. They have

01:20:14.840 --> 01:20:25.840
no knowledge, nothing, they just know Bible which also is so superficial. There is no

01:20:25.840 --> 01:20:41.840
depth in their life, nothing, self-certification. There's no certificate in Sahaja Yoga. If

01:20:41.840 --> 01:20:48.840
you are born again you will know yourself and then you have to become. It's a becoming

01:20:48.840 --> 01:20:58.840
that is important, that's a fact. Be careful about born again Christians, oh we have had

