enough of them. They felt quite challenged about Sahaja Yoga because everywhere we went

01:21:04.840 --> 01:21:09.840
they attacked us, everywhere they tried to attack us but when we went to Australia the

01:21:09.840 --> 01:21:14.840
Australians said, now you have done enough of yours, you have got anything from you,

01:21:14.840 --> 01:21:20.840
better they go away. So then they went away. But they are so self deceived also, they live

01:21:20.840 --> 01:21:34.840
with self deception, they know they haven't got anything. What have you got? All right,

01:21:34.840 --> 01:21:40.840
now Gregoire has said, I'm this, I'm that, all right, don't believe in Him, you must get

01:21:40.840 --> 01:21:51.840
something out of Me.

