What is the purpose of our sould. inthe material form?

01:23:26.688 --> 01:23:42.840
Oh, it's a long story. Human beings created the purpose, in a way like a diamond lost

01:23:42.840 --> 01:23:52.840
in the mire. We can say Adam and Eve, it started. There would have been no need to

01:23:52.840 --> 01:24:02.840
go through all this, but human beings wanted to know everything. They wanted to know the

01:24:02.840 --> 01:24:11.840
sting of a scorpion, they wanted to know the bite of a snake and then they wanted to come

01:24:11.840 --> 01:24:17.840
to God. All right, you have your own way, you have freedom. That's freedom nobody can

01:24:17.840 --> 01:24:23.840
take away, that's given to you, do what you like. So instead of eating your food directly

01:24:23.840 --> 01:24:34.840
like this, as I say, they started eating. What can you do? That's the human doing, not

01:24:34.840 --> 01:24:47.840
of God. It could have been very short circuited but it was so, all right. But that doesn't

01:24:47.840 --> 01:24:59.840
mean that your body is not required. Everything is required very much because the process

01:24:59.840 --> 01:25:06.840
is such. Supposing if you have a chance of making a fruit, a seed into a fruit, just

01:25:06.840 --> 01:25:11.840
in the laboratory, put the seed and it becomes the fruit. All right, then you don't have

01:25:11.840 --> 01:25:23.840
the whole process. But if the process is this way, better have it. Next, next time one can

01:25:23.840 --> 01:25:30.840
try that. But let's finish the process now. We're coming to the end of it. There's a

01:25:30.840 --> 01:25:46.840
trouble now we can't go back, can we? We are, I mean, trying to. We cannot. All right.

