01:26:49.840 --> 01:27:03.840
all right? Let's differentiate it. And then the soul is, all the five elements that are

01:27:03.840 --> 01:27:14.840
within us, they form the soul. And the light of the soul is the spirit, all right? No,

01:27:14.840 --> 01:27:21.840
no, no. But it doesn't transform from one to another. There's no transformation between

01:27:21.840 --> 01:27:31.840
this to that, all right? So today's mind becomes a spirit. Next life, as you are saying, how?

01:27:31.840 --> 01:27:42.840
