01:27:42.840 --> 01:27:53.840
root, to the self root, all right? Through the mind it acquires the understanding, the

01:27:53.840 --> 01:28:03.840
logic that you have to ascend. But it doesn't come out of your mind. It comes out of the

01:28:03.840 --> 01:28:12.840
mind of God Almighty, the Spirit, which is untarnishable, unchangeable. But by following

01:28:12.840 --> 01:28:22.840
your mind you realize that mind is not the last one. Or same with emotions. So many people

01:28:22.840 --> 01:28:27.840
who have failed in their emotional life, in a way, are specially blessed because they

01:28:27.840 --> 01:28:43.840
give up that kind of a madness and achieve Spirit. But it's not the same. It's very

01:28:43.840 --> 01:28:51.840
detached. It's not attached to any elements. Spirit is detached from all emotions. It can

01:28:51.840 --> 01:29:05.840
see everything but is detached. I followed your question, all right, isn't it? You

01:29:05.840 --> 01:29:16.840
understood it? You got your answer, all right? That's it, I'm happy. It's a good question

01:29:16.840 --> 01:29:26.840
but it was rather abridged form of a question but I managed it somehow. Now I'm happy

01:29:26.840 --> 01:29:33.840
because sometimes, you know, you people are so alert that you ask very nice questions

01:29:33.840 --> 01:29:47.840
but I'm not so intelligent, I must confess, as you people are because I don't use My

01:29:47.840 --> 01:30:04.840
mind at all. But you can reach the point very easily if you have your Spirit intact

01:30:04.840 --> 01:30:11.840
because it's light. Intelligence, if it is pure intelligence, what you call, that's

01:30:11.840 --> 01:30:19.840
the intelligence of the Spirit. You just reach the point, exactly. But the intelligence

01:30:19.840 --> 01:30:25.840
that we understand is very different, you see. It plays with the words, it baffles you,

01:30:25.840 --> 01:30:38.840
it's brilliant, your eyes can get completely shut with that. But it's not pure intelligence.

01:30:38.840 --> 01:30:59.840
Pure intelligence just gives you the absolute essence of everything. That's the intelligence

01:30:59.840 --> 01:31:16.840
of the Spirit, not of the mind.

