Sahaja Yogis should move from the second row and let people who are new should sit there.

01:37:32.020 --> 01:37:38.020
Please move from the second and the first row also, I mean.

01:37:55.506 --> 01:37:59.840
Please can you just, as I said, put your two feet on the ground straight without crossing

01:37:59.840 --> 01:38:04.840
the legs and put your two hands with the palm upwards in the direction of Shri Mataji.

01:38:04.840 --> 01:38:08.840
If you are sitting on the ground there's nothing to worry about the feet being on the

01:38:08.840 --> 01:38:13.840
ground. Then you are on the ground but those who are sitting on the chair, please put both

01:38:13.840 --> 01:38:19.840
your feet like this on the Mother Earth because she sucks in the problems you have and put

01:38:19.922 --> 01:38:23.840
both the hands like this towards Me.

01:38:38.840 --> 01:38:43.840
Now you have to close your eyes, just close your eyes.

01:38:53.588 --> 01:39:01.840
You don't open your eyes till I tell you to open your eyes. So you just keep your eyes

01:39:01.840 --> 01:39:03.840
shut.

01:39:07.840 --> 01:39:18.840
Now left hand is symbolic of our desire, desire power. So we are putting our desire, left

01:39:18.840 --> 01:39:29.840
hand, asking for our Self-realization. So keep it all the time, left hand towards Me.

01:39:30.840 --> 01:39:39.840
Right hand is the power of action, Kriya shakti. So you have to use the right hand for that

01:39:39.840 --> 01:39:48.840
and so you have to put your right hand onto different centers which I will explain to

01:39:48.840 --> 01:39:55.840
you very, in a very simple way and you'll be able to understand that you have to put

01:39:55.840 --> 01:40:01.840
your hand on these centers, helping your Kundalini to rise.

01:40:01.840 --> 01:40:10.840
Now we are working out only on the left hand side of our centers with our right hand. So

01:40:10.840 --> 01:40:17.840
the left hand is towards Me and the right hand goes onto different centers that we have,

01:40:17.840 --> 01:40:26.840
as simple as that. The first one is the one what we call is the seat of the Spirit which

01:40:26.840 --> 01:40:35.840
is the heart, which is on the left hand side. So please put your left hand towards Me all

01:40:35.840 --> 01:40:50.840
the time and the right hand on the heart. Now just on the heart. Now at this place you

01:40:50.840 --> 01:41:03.840
have to ask Me a very fundamental question, Mother, if you call Me Shri Mataji, Her Mother

01:41:03.840 --> 01:41:13.840
is the same, Mother, am I the Spirit? Is a fundamental question, just ask Me. Mother,

01:41:13.840 --> 01:41:40.840
am I the Spirit? Ask this question three times, Mother, am I the Spirit?

01:41:40.840 --> 01:41:47.840
So one has to know that if you become the Spirit you become your own guide, you become

01:41:47.840 --> 01:41:52.840
your own guru. This is all created by the great prophets and great gurus within you,

01:41:52.840 --> 01:42:01.840
the possibility. So now after this you take down your right hand onto your stomach on

01:42:01.840 --> 01:42:17.840
the left hand side. This is the center of mastery, mastery of the Divine power, the

01:42:17.840 --> 01:42:26.840
technique, how to use it. So here you have to ask another question, relevant with the

01:42:26.840 --> 01:42:33.840
first one, that if I am the Spirit, am I my own master? Ask a question now three times,

01:42:33.840 --> 01:42:41.840
Mother, am I my own master? Put your left hand towards Me and right hand on the left

01:42:41.840 --> 01:42:52.840
hand side of your stomach in the upper part. In the upper part of your stomach on the left

01:42:52.840 --> 01:42:59.840
hand side, please put your right hand and press it. And here you ask Me a question three

01:42:59.840 --> 01:43:14.840
times, Mother, am I my own master? Am I my own guide? Am I my own guru? This is the blessings

01:43:14.840 --> 01:43:40.840
of the real sadhgurus. Three times.

01:43:40.840 --> 01:43:51.840
Now please take your hand in the lower part of your abdomen on the left hand side. Now

01:43:51.840 --> 01:44:02.840
press it hard. This is the center that works out. First one was the master. This is the

01:44:02.840 --> 01:44:17.840
center that works out, the Divine technique of the true knowledge, of the pure knowledge.

01:44:17.840 --> 01:44:30.840
So now ask a question. In a way it's not a question but a request, because unless and

01:44:30.840 --> 01:44:39.840
until you ask for it, I cannot do it, I cannot cross your freedom. So here you say, Mother,

01:44:39.840 --> 01:44:50.840
please may I have the pure knowledge? Mother, may I have the pure knowledge? Say it three

01:44:50.840 --> 01:45:00.840
times. Mother, may I have the pure knowledge? Six times, because this center has got six

01:45:00.840 --> 01:45:09.840
petals. Now this you are asking to initiate the Kundalini, to awaken the Kundalini. When

01:45:09.840 --> 01:45:16.840
you ask for it, because it's such an absolute question, the Kundalini awakens. You have

01:45:16.840 --> 01:45:30.840
to request Her.

01:45:30.840 --> 01:45:55.840
Now, again raise your hand to the upper portion or upper area of the stomach, on the left

01:45:55.840 --> 01:46:07.840
hand side, at the center of the mastery. Here you press it hard and say with full confidence

01:46:07.840 --> 01:46:21.840
for the Kundalini to rise, to open the center with full assertion, Mother, I am my own master.

01:46:21.840 --> 01:46:40.840
Mother, I am my own master. You have to say this ten times, because there are ten masters

01:46:40.840 --> 01:46:50.840
within us, who have built up our ten centers, subplexuses of these solar plexus. So we have

01:46:50.840 --> 01:47:14.774
to say ten times, with full assertion, Mother, I am my own master.

01:47:30.874 --> 01:47:39.813
Now, raise your right hand on to the heart.

01:47:39.840 --> 01:47:49.840
Here again, with full confidence within yourself, forgetting all your past, forgetting all your

01:47:49.840 --> 01:47:59.840
problems, with full confidence and assertion, you have to say, Mother, I am the Spirit.

01:47:59.840 --> 01:48:06.840
You have to say it twelve times, Mother, I am the Spirit. You are the Spirit, no doubt

01:48:06.840 --> 01:48:09.793
about it.

01:48:18.710 --> 01:48:30.840
Believe in yourself, have faith in yourself. Know that you are the Spirit and nothing else.

01:49:25.390 --> 01:49:30.746
Now, raise your right hand in the corner of your head.

01:49:30.840 --> 01:49:43.840
If you have left shoulder and your neck from the front, this is the most difficult center

01:49:43.840 --> 01:49:51.840
that we have in the West, because people believe in something called the guilt, and all the

01:49:51.840 --> 01:50:04.840
time they feel guilty for nothing at all. So put it in the corner of the neck and the

01:50:04.840 --> 01:50:19.840
shoulder, press it hard on the backbone, hard. This is the worst center we have in the West,

01:50:19.840 --> 01:50:26.840
that we feel guilty for nothing at all. What is the feeling guilty? You are the Spirit.

01:50:26.840 --> 01:50:36.840
How can Spirit make mistakes? And God is the ocean of love and compassion, but above all

01:50:36.840 --> 01:50:44.840
He's the ocean of forgiveness. What guilt can you have? What mistakes can you commit

01:50:44.840 --> 01:50:53.840
that His power of forgiveness cannot forgive? You are not to be guilty. Forget My lecture,

01:50:53.840 --> 01:51:18.248
forget everything, you are the pure, immaculate Spirit. You are sat-chit-ananda. You are the source

01:51:18.278 --> 01:51:43.820
of all that is joy.

01:51:47.190 --> 01:51:56.786
Better. You have to say this sixteen times, Mother, I am not guilty. Sixteen times, press

01:51:56.840 --> 01:52:19.840
it hard and say it sixteen times.

01:52:25.910 --> 01:52:43.770
So in the beginning it was terrible.

01:52:52.260 --> 01:53:03.840
Now take this hand and put it across your forehead, please. Stretch your left hand towards

01:53:03.840 --> 01:53:15.840
Me. At this point, not how many times, but from your heart you have to say, Mother, I

01:53:15.840 --> 01:53:26.840
forgive everyone. Something that's very difficult to forgive, it's a myth, because

01:53:26.840 --> 01:53:31.840
whether you forgive or not forgive you don't do anything about it. But if you don't forgive

01:53:31.840 --> 01:53:39.840
then you play into the wrong hands. So please say, Mother, I forgive. That's the greatest

01:53:39.840 --> 01:53:50.840
weapon you have. Mother, I forgive.

01:53:50.840 --> 01:54:17.840
Everyone, first of all yourself. Now on the back of your head, hold it tight. Now for

01:54:17.840 --> 01:54:28.840
your own consolation you can say that, O God Almighty, or O my Kundalini the Mother,

01:54:28.840 --> 01:54:46.840
if I have done anything wrong in Your glory, in Your name, please forgive me. Not to feel

01:54:46.840 --> 01:54:52.840
guilty at all, please don't feel guilty, but just say it out, don't count all your

01:54:52.840 --> 01:54:58.840
so-called sins, just forget it, forget it, forget it.

01:54:58.840 --> 01:55:10.840
Now, raise your hand on top of your head, on the fontanel bone area, stretch your palm

01:55:10.840 --> 01:55:17.840
and press it hard in a clockwise manner. Take your right hand on top of your head,

01:55:17.840 --> 01:55:27.840
on the fontanel bone area, which was a soft bone in your childhood, press it hard and

01:55:27.840 --> 01:55:39.840
here in a clockwise manner when you move it you have to say something which I cannot do

01:55:39.840 --> 01:55:46.840
it without it because you are free. So you have to say, Mother, I want my realization,

01:55:46.840 --> 01:55:53.840
I cannot force on you. So to say, I want my realization, Mother, please give me my self-realization.

01:55:53.840 --> 01:56:00.840
Just say that, press it hard, press it hard, stretch your palm on top of fontanel bone

01:56:00.840 --> 01:56:07.840
area. Now, seven times.

01:56:08.470 --> 01:56:21.339
[Shri Mataji blows into the microphone]

01:56:57.012 --> 01:57:01.262
Now bring down your right hand, please.

01:57:01.840 --> 01:57:13.840
The most valuable moment of your life and the most precious, important happening. Now,

01:57:13.840 --> 01:57:19.840
please place your right hand towards Me and left hand on top of your head, bending the

01:57:19.840 --> 01:57:27.840
head about, say, three, four inches and move the hand and see if there's any cool breeze

01:57:27.840 --> 01:57:31.840
coming out of your own head, please.

01:57:34.840 --> 01:57:43.840
It was really nice to have this seminar organized here at such a short notice with no proper

01:57:43.840 --> 01:57:49.840
planning or anything and you got such a nice place also. Spontaneously the whole thing

01:57:49.840 --> 01:57:59.840
has worked out and everything is managed. But today you saw the new people who came

01:57:59.840 --> 01:58:14.840
were an example of the dearth of seeking in this country, or maybe. There is some sort

01:58:14.840 --> 01:58:26.840
of lacking on the part of English Sahaja Yogis also. The way that, because I'm here, people

01:58:26.840 --> 01:58:35.840
take things for granted. Or maybe that a few like Gavin and others are very anxious, trying

01:58:35.840 --> 01:58:46.840
to do their level best to do this. And I think on two points might be we are failing.

01:58:46.840 --> 01:58:57.840
One point is that we all must know what have we done for Sahaja Yoga. Some people take

01:58:57.840 --> 01:59:06.840
two or three posters and post them, then they think they have done everything. No.

01:59:06.840 --> 01:59:14.840
You have to do much more than anywhere else because you are placed in this important thing

01:59:14.840 --> 01:59:22.840
called the heart. Everybody has had an advantage of Sahaja Yoga, has been helped a lot. We

01:59:23.840 --> 01:59:31.840
have to think what have we done for Sahaja Yoga. It has done so much for us, what have

01:59:31.840 --> 01:59:41.840
we done for Sahaja Yoga. That's very important. So then there should be, I think I was expressing

01:59:41.840 --> 01:59:50.840
that anxiety which the people who are your leaders and those who are worried about Sahaja

01:59:50.840 --> 02:00:01.840
Yoga in England. And My lecture, the whole lecture has that tremendous concern. And then

02:00:01.840 --> 02:00:06.840
we have to think what have we done. We have houses, we have places, we have ashrams, we

02:00:06.840 --> 02:00:12.840
have families, we have wives, we have everything. And the Sahaja Yoga still if it is by the

02:00:12.840 --> 02:00:19.840
way then this is the result. You get twenty nonsensical, arrogant people, don't get

02:00:19.840 --> 02:00:27.840
realization, some of them get it and get out. So I think this is on one side is this that

02:00:27.840 --> 02:00:32.840
what have we done for Sahaja Yoga. There should be a, in other countries I'm not there. So

02:00:32.840 --> 02:00:39.840
for them when I go there, even for four, five days, the whole place is filled with My, the

02:00:39.840 --> 02:00:46.840
whole place is filled with My posters, the whole place. It has to be done, every time

02:00:46.840 --> 02:00:54.840
has been. The whole of London should have been today filled with My posters. I mean

02:00:54.840 --> 02:01:03.840
anybody who goes to say Switzerland or to Rome or to Paris, they tell Me, Indians, that

02:01:03.840 --> 02:01:12.840
we saw your posters all over the place. But never has happened in London. Now I hope this

02:01:12.840 --> 02:01:20.840
is not the last program, public program in England. But still one has to work very hard.

02:01:20.840 --> 02:01:28.840
All of you should think what you can do because everybody has taken things in their own style

02:01:28.840 --> 02:01:35.840
like the leaders are working hard, they are all trying to do things and arrange things,

02:01:35.840 --> 02:01:43.840
all that. But what have you done is the point. Now some people have had failures, say for

02:01:43.840 --> 02:01:49.840
example some people had failures with the officials and for the government or with the

02:01:49.840 --> 02:01:54.840
TV, doesn't matter. We know we have failed there. But advertising, postering, talking

02:01:54.840 --> 02:02:02.840
about it, going around it, all that can be done. This one part is very good in this respect

02:02:02.840 --> 02:02:08.840
is that outside London things are working out better. But how many of you have been

02:02:08.840 --> 02:02:20.840
doing that? Very few. The same party goes here, same party has to do it all the time.

02:02:20.840 --> 02:02:27.840
Now, now this is one side of the picture is that, that the advertising and all that

02:02:27.840 --> 02:02:35.840
has to be done more intensely, extensively. And everybody must offer their full support

02:02:35.840 --> 02:02:43.840
and services. On the seminar side you are all very good, everything is done well, I

02:02:43.840 --> 02:02:48.840
agree. So many things are, because we have to do so many things together. But still you

02:02:49.840 --> 02:02:57.840
being the heart you have to be like that, what can you do? That's one part of it.

02:02:57.840 --> 02:03:04.840
The second part of it I feel is, like we had in Hampstead about three hundred people and

02:03:04.840 --> 02:03:15.840
they came and what I've learnt is that when they came to the program nobody was sort of

02:03:15.840 --> 02:03:21.840
open hearted, sort of talked to them in that way as they should have. Some of you did but

02:03:21.840 --> 02:03:26.840
not all. Most of you are just sitting down. Like if they come to My house they'll just

02:03:26.840 --> 02:03:34.840
sit down, hands like this. You cannot, you cannot just do that, it's not done. Come

02:03:34.840 --> 02:03:40.840
to My house, sit down like this. Always they will come and sit down and put hands like

02:03:40.840 --> 02:03:49.840
this. You can't do like that. That shows you are very insular, very selfish and also

02:03:49.840 --> 02:03:59.840
in a way arrogant. You cannot take My vibrations without My permission, can you?

02:03:59.840 --> 02:04:08.840
So this is suggestive of one thing, that what we do is to take things for granted and we,

02:04:08.840 --> 02:04:15.840
when we talk to others also it takes time for an Englishman to get up. That's the

02:04:15.840 --> 02:04:23.840
thing is. Now the quality of this is this, that in English do not want to interfere with

02:04:23.840 --> 02:04:28.840
anyone, they want to leave them alone. It's not the bad thing. They want that why should

02:04:28.840 --> 02:04:34.840
we interfere, aggress, that's the point is. But that's not the point now, we have

02:04:34.840 --> 02:04:39.840
to aggress. This is the thing I'm bringing you to. That means you don't mean that.

02:04:39.840 --> 02:04:45.840
But what you mean is that not to interfere. See they don't discuss religion in England,

02:04:45.840 --> 02:04:51.840
no, you are not supposed to say these things. You are not to discuss whether you are a miss

02:04:51.840 --> 02:04:57.840
or a missus. You are not to say whether you have children or not. If you ask somebody

02:04:57.840 --> 02:05:02.840
a question, you have you got children, that means the most offensive thing. You are not

02:05:02.840 --> 02:05:08.840
to discuss anybody's family. There are so many don'ts in this country so that we do

02:05:08.840 --> 02:05:18.840
not also sort of get up worried that maybe this may be taken as an interference. But

02:05:18.840 --> 02:05:25.840
just the opposite are Americans. They will go up to the great grandfather and up to the

02:05:25.840 --> 02:05:33.840
whole progeny to find out. So interference should be forgotten, there should be no fear

02:05:33.840 --> 02:05:39.840
about them. But open your heart and talk to them openly with an open heart. But people

02:05:39.840 --> 02:05:45.840
receive back. Once they receive back, others also somehow or other get frightened because

02:05:45.840 --> 02:05:53.840
they think you are just like them. You have to be different to attract them.

02:05:53.840 --> 02:06:00.840
So amongst English Sahaja Yogis there are some who are very anxious, very much worried,

02:06:00.840 --> 02:06:07.840
they are being so much, working it out. Some of them are really indifferent and the middle

02:06:07.840 --> 02:06:15.840
part is those who are still trying to see how far to go, how far not to go, you have

02:06:15.840 --> 02:06:23.840
to be aggressive about it. I mean as if now I feel the English have aggressed so much

02:06:23.840 --> 02:06:29.840
that now they are so fed up with aggressiveness. That's the thing I want you to have today,

02:06:29.840 --> 02:06:36.840
to be aggress. Aggressiveness is the only way you can reach these people, otherwise

02:06:36.840 --> 02:06:42.840
they won't understand. And you have to talk to them on their faces. I have seen how people

02:06:42.840 --> 02:06:47.840
talk. If you talk to them like that they are all right. Unless and until you work out

02:06:47.840 --> 02:06:53.840
that way, when the people come, you talk to them in an aggressively loving manner. Do

02:06:53.840 --> 02:07:01.840
you understand that? Exuberance, just open out your heart. How come long, come long,

02:07:01.840 --> 02:07:07.840
where are you going, sit down, what do you want, you want. One minute Englishman will

02:07:07.840 --> 02:07:16.840
look like this, you see. Second minute, you must understand your own character that exists

02:07:16.840 --> 02:07:27.840
in those people also. If the language starts, I'm afraid. So aggressively compassionate,

02:07:27.840 --> 02:07:42.840
aggressively loving, aggressively open hearted. Non-interference and all those ideas are out

02:07:42.840 --> 02:07:59.840
of date now, finished. Now openness, no arrogance, no anger, but openness. Aggressive innocence

02:07:59.840 --> 02:08:11.840
people, like children are. Children are so aggressively innocent that you like it. I

02:08:11.840 --> 02:08:16.840
mean if they catch hold of you, they'll all come and jump on your body and sleep on

02:08:16.840 --> 02:08:28.840
top of you, kissing you all over. That's how. You have to be aggressively loving and

02:08:28.840 --> 02:08:34.840
aggressively good. What you want, you want something to eat, you want this, that, that.

02:08:34.840 --> 02:08:41.840
They'll be surprised how these English people have become like this. So on these two things

02:08:41.840 --> 02:08:50.840
we fail and this anguish and this anxiety that I have is one of the expressions of the

02:08:50.840 --> 02:08:56.840
modern times, you must know, is of the modern times, you see. Because modern times are so

02:08:56.840 --> 02:09:02.840
funny that if you click it, you click it and if you don't click it, missed. It's so

02:09:02.840 --> 02:09:10.840
important, so precarious is the word, so precarious. At this time if you don't click it, it's finished.

02:09:10.840 --> 02:09:20.840
So I find everyone is capable of doing lots of things for Sahaja Yoga. But

02:09:20.840 --> 02:09:26.840
what have we done for Sahaja Yoga? Nice in the seminar to come and enjoy, it's good idea,

02:09:26.840 --> 02:09:33.840
I enjoy Sahaja Yogis, Mother is collecting them. One of the examples is that from the

02:09:33.840 --> 02:09:40.840
other countries people come. They are sick, they have problems, this, that. Immediately

02:09:40.840 --> 02:09:51.840
telephone will ring Me up saying, Mother somebody has come with ten bhoots and fifteen babhoots.

02:09:51.840 --> 02:10:02.840
So what? When should that person see you? I said, the person or the bhoots? And the bhoots

02:10:02.840 --> 02:10:13.840
only come, the person is missing. At least you can reduce some numbers and then send

02:10:13.840 --> 02:10:24.840
such a person. Now I've started using the hearth of My house instead of the candle.

02:10:24.840 --> 02:10:32.840
Now will you please look after the bhoots of the people when they come? And among you

02:10:32.840 --> 02:10:38.840
are, there are many like that. Your children are caught up, some of the wives are caught

02:10:38.840 --> 02:10:47.840
up, some of the husbands are caught up, but nobody pays attention, carrying on with them,

02:10:47.840 --> 02:10:55.840
sometimes even supporting. And just I see them, even staying in ashrams I must say,

02:10:55.840 --> 02:11:03.840
some of them are really bhootish and troublesome. And you think that you have to tolerate, there's

02:11:03.840 --> 02:11:10.840
no crucifixion needed anymore. If somebody has a bhoot, better tell that person you are

02:11:10.840 --> 02:11:17.840
catching. I mean I don't want to tell, but you know what happens to Me? My hands and

02:11:17.840 --> 02:11:24.840
My feet they all go crazy, and there's a bhootish person around, so I just run away.

02:11:24.840 --> 02:11:29.840
In the same way it should happen to you and you should try to correct that person, but

02:11:29.840 --> 02:11:36.840
nobody bothers. You see because you think correction will be too much, oh maybe he might

02:11:36.840 --> 02:11:43.840
feel hurt and he'll run away. Let him run away, take two running jumps and go to hell.

02:11:43.840 --> 02:11:50.840
But the whole thing should be a concern and anxiety and loving way, then you will attract

